ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.24                 Enzyme
NAME        1,4-alpha-glucan 6-alpha-glucosyltransferase;
            oligoglucan-branching glycosyltransferase;
            1,4-alpha-D-glucan 6-alpha-D-glucosyltransferase;
            T-enzyme;
            D-glucosyltransferase;
            1,4-alpha-D-glucan:1,4-alpha-D-glucan(D-glucose) 6-alpha-D-glucosyltransferase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     (1->4)-alpha-D-glucan:(1->4)-alpha-D-glucan(D-glucose) 6-alpha-D-glucosyltransferase
REACTION    Transfers an alpha-D-glucosyl residue in a (1->4)-alpha-D-glucan to the primary hydroxy group of glucose, free or combined in a (1->4)-alpha-D-glucan
HISTORY     EC 2.4.1.24 created 1965
